{"tid":1258822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最好就長期閂左個警崗佢","createTime":"2019-06-26T09:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T10:07:52.000Z","uid":27608,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d381d9c4a12095cc26ccbb55732c658154c4756","tid":1258822,"uid":27608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"發夢時警崗就係d警犬蛇王嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD狗一接完波無野做就會去個到呑Pot打機hea<br />\n多人嘅時候可以有成6隻狗係警崗白布入面打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以最好將計就計<br />\n汁鬼左個警崗佢<br />\n等d狗唔可以係入面嘆冷氣<br />\n要佢地係大熱天時或者落大雨嘅時候係街上面激到扎扎跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f3c616cfb592aea6955b651e34b72c0453605e","tid":1258822,"uid":27608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f07671e51c52da6505300f0318d438bd80bf9c7","tid":1258822,"uid":27608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aee80f605f0d786c9ef1486bb1005cababa1d07","tid":1258822,"uid":216326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"用黎擺雜物得啦 都無用既"}]}